<p>Unbelievably good biking conditions <a href="http://www.google.com/maps?f=d&amp;hl=en&amp;saddr=euclid+and+broadway+boulder,+co&amp;daddr=16th+and+baseline+rd+boulder,+co+to:1138+Flagstaff+Dr,+Boulder,+CO+80302+(Flagstaff+House+Restaurant)+%4040.003550,-105.303842&amp;sll=40.002043,-105.290565&amp;sspn=0.032217,0.061798&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;om=1&amp;z=14">out there</a> today!  Dave's bike better get fixed soon...I'm getting lonely!</p>
<p>I had a nice slow warm-up on Baseline, made a medium pace on Flagstaff (no throat clearing or red zone moments), and even slipped the gate on the Amphitheater Road to top off a good ride.</p>
